properties.areaDesc: Delaware Bay waters south of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE; Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 10 at 3:19PM EST until February 10 at 6:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 15 to 20 knots with gusts up to 30
knots and seas 4 to 5 feet are expected.

* WHERE...Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to
Slaughter Beach DE and Delaware Bay waters south of East Point
NJ to Slaughter Beach DE.

* WHEN...Until 6:00 PM this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 PM EST THIS EVENING
